@startuml request-lifecycle
' ============================================================
' AlharisTech Platform — Request Lifecycle
' Full HTTP request trace: Browser → CDN → Next.js → API → DB
' ============================================================

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif"
skinparam defaultFontSize 9

skinparam participant {
  BackgroundColor #D4E6F1
  BorderColor #2980B9
  FontSize 9
}

skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #FDEBD0
  BorderColor #E67E22
}

skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #D5F5E3
  BorderColor #27AE60
  FontSize 9
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FEF9E7
  BorderColor #F1C40F
  FontSize 8
}

skinparam box {
  BackgroundColor #F4F6F7
  BorderColor #AAB7B8
  FontSize 10
  FontStyle bold
}

title **AlharisTech Platform — Full Request Lifecycle**
title **دورة حياة الطلب: HTTP Request → Response**

actor "Browser\nمتصفح المستخدم" as Browser

box "Edge Network" #E8F0FE
  participant "CDN\nVercel/CloudFront" as CDN
endbox

box "Frontend (Next.js)" #FDEBD0
  participant "Next.js Server\nSSR/ISR/SSG" as NextServer
  participant "TanStack Query\nClient Cache" as TanstackCache
  participant "Next.js Middleware\nAuth + Locale" as NextMiddleware
  participant "SDK Client\n@alharistech/sdk" as SDK
endbox

box "API Layer (NestJS)" #D5F5E3
  participant "API Gateway\nNestJS" as Gateway
  participant "Middleware\nRequest ID, CORS, Helmet" as APIMiddleware
  participant "Guards\nJWT Auth + RBAC" as Guards
  participant "Interceptors\nLogging, Response Wrap" as Interceptors
  participant "Pipes\nZod Validation" as Pipes
  participant "Controller\nREST / GraphQL" as Controller
  participant "Application\nService (Use Case)" as AppService
  participant "Domain\nService (Business Logic)" as DomainService
  participant "Repository\nData Access (Prisma)" as Repository
endbox

box "Data Layer" #F5EEF8
  database "Redis\nCache / Session" as Redis
  database "PostgreSQL\nPrimary Database" as DB
  database "S3/MinIO\nFile Storage" as S3
endbox

box "External Services" #FDEDEC
  participant "Payment Gateway\nStripe/Moyasar" as Payment
  participant "Email/SMS\nProviders" as Notify
endbox

== REQUEST FLOW — Client → CDN → API → Database → Response ==

Browser -> CDN : GET https://alharistech.com/ar/orders/123

alt CDN Cache Hit (static assets / ISR page)
  CDN -> CDN : Check cache key\n(URL + headers)
  note right of CDN
    **CDN Caching Strategy:**
    · Static assets: 1 hour
    · ISR pages: revalidate on demand
    · API responses: no-cache for auth'd data
    · ETag / Last-Modified headers
  endnote
  CDN --> Browser : 200 OK (cached)\nAge: 3600, X-Cache: HIT
else CDN Cache Miss (dynamic/authenticated)
  CDN -> NextServer : Proxy request

  NextServer -> NextMiddleware : Middleware runs
  NextMiddleware -> NextMiddleware : 1. Parse locale from path (/ar/...)\n2. Check auth cookie (refreshToken)\n3. Set X-Tenant-Id header\n4. Apply CSP headers

  alt Auth required and no valid cookie
    NextMiddleware --> NextServer : Redirect to /ar/login
    NextServer --> Browser : 302 /ar/login
  else Auth valid or public route
    NextMiddleware -> NextServer : Continue

    NextServer -> NextServer : Decide rendering:\nSSR vs ISR vs SSG

    alt SSR (dynamic data needed)
      NextServer -> TanstackCache : Check query cache\n(queryKey, staleTime)

      alt Cache hit (fresh)
        TanstackCache --> NextServer : Cached data
        note right of TanstackCache
          **TanStack Query Cache:**
          · staleTime: 5 minutes
          · gcTime: 30 minutes
          · In-memory (server-side)
          · Cache key: [resource, params]
        endnote
      else Cache miss or stale
        TanstackCache -> SDK : fetch data (stale → revalidate)
        SDK -> Gateway : GET /api/v1/orders/123\nAuthorization: Bearer <jwt>\nX-Request-Id: uuid\nX-Tenant-Id: tenant_xxx

        Gateway -> APIMiddleware : Request enters API

        APIMiddleware -> APIMiddleware : 1. Generate/X-Request-Id\n2. CORS check\n3. Helmet security headers\n4. Compression

        APIMiddleware -> Guards : Pass to guards chain

        Guards -> Guards : **JwtAuthGuard**:\n· Extract JWT from header\n· Verify signature + expiry\n· Decode payload → req.user

        alt JWT invalid/expired
          Guards --> Gateway : 401 Unauthorized
          Gateway --> SDK : 401
          SDK -> SDK : Trigger token refresh\nPOST /api/v1/auth/refresh
          SDK -> Gateway : Retry original request\nwith new accessToken
        else JWT valid
          Guards -> Guards : **RolesGuard**:\nCheck user.role ∈ allowed roles

          alt Role insufficient
            Guards --> Gateway : 403 Forbidden
            Gateway --> SDK : 403
          else Role allowed
            Guards -> Guards : **PermissionGuard**:\nCheck required perms ∈ user.permissions

            alt Permission denied
              Guards --> Gateway : 403 Forbidden
              Gateway --> SDK : 403
            else Permission granted
              Guards -> Interceptors : Pass to interceptors

              Interceptors -> Interceptors : **LoggingInterceptor**:\nLog: method, path, userId, requestId

              Interceptors -> Interceptors : **ResponseTimeInterceptor**:\nStart timer

              Interceptors -> Pipes : Pass to validation pipes

              Pipes -> Pipes : **ZodValidationPipe**:\n· Parse & validate params/body\n· whitelist: strip unknowns\n· forbidNonWhitelisted\n· transform types

              alt Validation fails
                Pipes --> Gateway : 400 Bad Request\n{ error, details }
                Gateway --> SDK : 400
              else Validation passes
                Pipes -> Controller : Validated DTO

                Controller -> AppService : getOrderById(id, user)

                AppService -> AppService : Orchestrate use case:\n· Validate order exists\n· Check data-level access\n  (customer can only see own)

                AppService -> Redis : Check application cache\nKEY: "order:123"

                alt Cache hit (Redis)
                  Redis --> AppService : Cached data
                else Cache miss
                  AppService -> DomainService : Process business logic

                  DomainService -> DomainService : · Apply business rules\n· Calculate derived values\n· Enforce invariants

                  DomainService -> Repository : findById(id)

                  Repository -> Repository : Build Prisma query:\n· WHERE id = ?\n· Include relations\n· Apply data-level scope

                  Repository -> DB : SELECT * FROM orders\nWHERE id = '123'\nAND customer_id = 'user-456'

                  alt Database read replica available
                    note right of DB
                      **Read/Write Split:**
                      · Reads → Read Replica
                      · Writes → Primary
                      · Managed by Prisma
                    endnote
                  end

                  DB --> Repository : Order row + relations

                  Repository --> DomainService : Order entity

                  DomainService --> AppService : Domain result

                  AppService -> Redis : SET "order:123" <data>\nEX 300 (5 min TTL)
                end

                AppService --> Controller : Order DTO

                Controller -> Controller : Serialize response\n(remove sensitive fields)

                Controller --> Interceptors : Response data

                Interceptors -> Interceptors : **WrapResponseInterceptor**:\nWrap in envelope:\n{ data, meta: { requestId, timestamp } }

                Interceptors -> Interceptors : **ResponseTimeInterceptor**:\nAdd X-Response-Time header

                Interceptors --> Gateway : Formatted response

                Gateway -> APIMiddleware : Response passes back\nthrough middleware

                APIMiddleware -> APIMiddleware : Add security headers\n· X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff\n· X-Frame-Options: DENY\n· Referrer-Policy: strict-origin\n· Strict-Transport-Security

                Gateway --> SDK : 200 { data: { order },\n  meta: { requestId, timestamp } }
                SDK -> SDK : Validate response\nagainst Zod schema
                SDK --> TanstackCache : Typed response

                TanstackCache -> TanstackCache : Update cache
                TanstackCache --> NextServer : Data

                NextServer -> NextServer : Render page with data\n(React Server Components)
                NextServer --> CDN : Rendered HTML
                CDN -> CDN : Optionally cache\n(ISR with revalidation)
                CDN --> Browser : 200 OK — Full rendered page
              end
            end
          end
        end
      end
    else ISR (static page, revalidate on demand)
      NextServer --> CDN : Cached/regenerated HTML
      CDN --> Browser : 200 OK
    end
  end
end

== CACHING SUMMARY ==

note over Browser, DB
  **AlharisTech Multi-Layer Caching Strategy:**
  |===
  | Layer | Technology | TTL | Scope |
  | **CDN** | Vercel/CloudFront | 1 hour | Static + ISR pages |
  | **HTTP** | ETag + Last-Modified | Per-resource | Conditional requests |
  | **TanStack Query** | In-memory (Next.js server) | 5 min staleTime | Per-page queries |
  | **Application Cache** | Redis | 5-15 min | API responses |
  | **Database Cache** | PostgreSQL Shared Buffers | Auto | Query plans + data |
  |===
endnote

@enduml
